<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Entrar ‚Äî Biblioteca Escolar</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <style>
    :root{
      --lib-green: #2e5f4f;
      --lib-green-dark: #254a41;
      --muted: #9aa4af;
      --panel: #fbfcfb;
    }
    body{
      min-height:100vh;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg,#f4f6f5 0%,#eef3f2 100%);
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      color:#1f2d2b;
      padding:2rem;
    }
    .form-panel{
      width:100%;
      max-width:520px;
      background:var(--panel);
      border:1px solid #e1e8e5;
      border-radius:12px;
      box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(17,24,23,0.08);
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    .brand{
      background: linear-gradient(90deg,var(--lib-green),var(--lib-green-dark));
      color:#fff;
      padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:.75rem;
    }
    .brand h2{ margin:0; font-size:1.125rem; font-weight:700; }
    .brand small{ opacity:.95; font-weight:600; }
    .panel-body{ padding:1.25rem 1.5rem; }
    .tab-pane h4{ margin-bottom:1rem; }
    .form-label{ font-weight:600; color:#24312f; }
    .btn-primary{
      background:var(--lib-green);
      border-color:var(--lib-green-dark);
    }
    .btn-success{
      background:var(--lib-green-dark);
      border-color:var(--lib-green-dark);
    }
    .form-help{
      font-size:.875rem;
      color:var(--muted);
    }
    .footer-note{
      text-align:center;
      padding: .75rem 1rem;
      font-size:.8rem;
      color:#5c6a67;
      border-top:1px solid #eef3f2;
      background:#fbfdfc;
    }
    @media (max-width:480px){
      .brand h2{ font-size:1rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="form-panel">
    <div class="brand">
      <span style="font-size:1.6rem;">üèõÔ∏è</span>
      <div>
        <h2>Biblioteca Escolar</h2>
        <small>Acesso ao cat√°logo e reservas</small>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel-body">
      <ul class="nav nav-tabs mb-3" id="tabForm" role="tablist">
        <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
          <button class="nav-link active" id="login-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#login" type="button" role="tab">Entrar</button>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
          <button class="nav-link" id="register-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#register" type="button" role="tab">Cadastrar</button>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="tab-content">
        <!-- Login -->
        <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="login" role="tabpanel">
          <h4>Login</h4>
          <form method="post" action="/usuario/login">
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="loginEmail" class="form-label">Email</label>
              <input name="email" type="email" class="form-control" id="loginEmail" placeholder="seu@exemplo.com" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="loginPassword" class="form-label">Senha</label>
              <input name="senha" type="password" class="form-control" id="loginPassword" placeholder="‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢" required>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
              <div class="form-check">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="remember" name="remember">
                <label class="form-check-label form-help" for="remember">Lembrar-me</label>
              </div>
              <a href="/usuario/recuperar" class="form-help">Esqueceu a senha?</a>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100">Entrar</button>
          </form>

          <!-- Voltar -->
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary w-100 mt-2">Voltar ao in√≠cio</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Cadastro -->
        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="register" role="tabpanel">
          <h4>Cadastro</h4>
          <form method="post" action="/usuario/register">
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="registerName" class="form-label">Nome completo</label>
              <input name="nome" type="text" class="form-control" id="registerName" placeholder="Seu nome" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="registerEmail" class="form-label">Email</label>
              <input name="email" type="email" class="form-control" id="registerEmail" placeholder="seu@exemplo.com" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="registerPassword" class="form-label">Senha</label>
              <input name="senha" type="password" class="form-control" id="registerPassword" placeholder="M√≠nimo 6 caracteres" required>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success w-100">Cadastrar</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-note">
      Ao se cadastrar voc√™ ter√° acesso a reservas, hist√≥rico e coment√°rios. ‚Ä¢ Biblioteca Escolar
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11"></script>

  <% if (message) { %>
    <script>
      Swal.fire({
        icon: '<%= message.type %>',
        text: '<%= message.value %>',
        confirmButtonColor: '#2e5f4f'
      });
    </script>
  <% } %>
</body>
</html>
